      "title": "Mahinda denied the quota related story",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa is still in the country. Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena said that I made a mistake during an interview with BBC.",
        "In a telephone interview to the Indian news service ANI, he denied that \"President Gotabaya Rajapaksa is not in the country but has gone to a nearby country and he will return to the country on Wednesday.\""
